cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.AI 

This paper deals with the optimization of network services, which involves the allocation of physical resources and dynamic re-routing of flows between service components. This falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI) and system and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper proposes a fully automated approach using algorithms, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Finally, the paper also involves the use of high-level abstraction and formalization of the problem, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
